ement","2026-05-12T10:51:05+0000","2026-07-01T06:27:49+0000","eb53ebaf-7be1-48a6-aca2-8a14b526b244","Essai gratuit",{"id":64,"type":56,"tags":65,"lang":14,"slug":66,"first_publication_date":67,"last_publication_date":68,"link_type":38,"key":69,"isBroken":40,"text":70,"variant":71},"aiEb6BYAAC0AdvTJ",[],"inscrivez-vous-","2026-06-04T06:32:33+0000","2026-06-23T13:18:36+0000","b4d404eb-b90c-4329-8c85-e6e98b411fb2","Inscriptions","Bouton",{"id":73,"uid":74,"url":75,"type":45,"href":76,"tags":77,"first_publication_date":78,"last_publication_date":79,"slugs":80,"linked_documents":81,"lang":14,"alternate_languages":82,"data":83},"agRmOBAAANw7T99e","le-hakama","\u002Ffocus\u002Fle-hakama","https:\u002F\u002Faikido-traditionnel-cotiere.cdn.prismic.io\u002Fapi\u002Fv2\u002Fdocuments\u002Fsearch?ref=akS-fBIAACsAR9AK&q=%5B%5B%3Ad+%3D+at%28document.id%2C+%22agRmOBAAANw7T99e%22%29+%5D%5D",[],"2026-05-13T11:57:46+0000","2026-05-13T12:27:15+0000",[74],[],[],{"title":84,"description":90,"cover":95,"slices":105,"meta_title":5,"meta_description":5,"meta_image":341},[85],{"type":86,"text":87,"spans":88,"direction":89},"heading1","Le hakama",[],"ltr",[91],{"type":92,"text":93,"spans":94,"direction":89},"paragraph","Le hakama comporte sept plis qui symbolisent les sert vertus du Budo. Le fait de porter le hakama montre que le pratiquant respecte ces vertus. Le pliage du hakama est donc très important.",[],{"dimensions":96,"alt":5,"copyright":5,"url":99,"id":100,"edit":101},{"width":97,"height":98},200,100,"https:\u002F\u002Fimages.prismic.io\u002Faikido-traditionnel-cotiere\u002FagRkbqYofJOwHLjT_Gemini_Generated_Image_gsw3rdgsw3rdgsw3.png?auto=format%2Ccompress&rect=674%2C655%2C1514%2C757&w=200&h=100","agRkbqYofJOwHLjT",{"x":102,"y":103,"zoom":104,"background":28},674,655,1.8600000000000003,[106,147,249,296,317],{"variation":107,"version":108,"items":109,"primary":110,"id":145,"slice_type":146,"slice_label":5},"default","initial",[],{"anchor":5,"title":111,"sub_title":114,"content":115,"image":118,"liens":126,"details":144,"iframe":5},[112],{"type":86,"text":87,"spans":113,"direction":89},[],[],[116],{"type":92,"text":93,"spans":117,"direction":89},[],{"dimensions":119,"alt":5,"copyright":5,"url":122,"id":100,"edit":123},{"width":120,"height":121},2816,1536,"https:\u002F\u002Fimages.prismic.io\u002Faikido-traditionnel-cotiere\u002FagRkbqYofJOwHLjT_Gemini_Generated_Image_gsw3rdgsw3rdgsw3.png?auto=format%2Ccompress&rect=678%2C663%2C1514%2C826&w=2816&h=1536",{"x":124,"y":125,"zoom":104,"background":28},678,663,[127,132,136,140],{"link_type":128,"key":129,"url":130,"text":131,"variant":71},"Web","4ac961ca-a532-4e58-bb70-8539840a5b88","#avant","Les plis à l'avant",{"link_type":128,"key":133,"url":134,"text":135,"variant":71},"e6f4dc6c-a810-43b9-9e1c-be7bc0080ad4","#arriere","Les plis à l'arrière",{"link_type":128,"key":137,"url":138,"text":139,"variant":71},"ef219df6-430e-45e3-a392-c181eef09ed7","#mettre","Comment mettre son hakama",{"link_type":128,"key":141,"url":142,"text":143,"variant":71},"e2b771c9-89ed-47b0-b7db-55a8805af7f2","#plier","Comment plier son hakama",[],"focus_content$e7a4542d-572f-433a-8b23-6391842c3426","focus_content",{"variation":107,"version":108,"items":148,"primary":149,"id":248,"slice_type":146,"slice_label":5},[],{"anchor":150,"title":151,"sub_title":152,"content":157,"image":158,"liens":159,"details":160,"iframe":5},"avant",[],[153],{"type":154,"text":155,"spans":156,"direction":89},"heading2","Les 5 plis à l'avant",[],[],{},[],[161,182,200,216,232],{"content_title":162,"content_punchline":167,"content_body":176,"content_image":180,"content_link":181},[163],{"type":164,"text":165,"spans":166,"direction":89},"heading3","Jin",[],[168],{"type":169,"text":170,"spans":171,"direction":89},"heading4","(djine) 仁",[172],{"start":173,"end":174,"type":175},8,9,"em",[177],{"type":92,"text":178,"spans":179,"direction":89},"la bienveillance, la générosité : Cette vertu demande une attitude pleine d’attention pour autrui, sans considération d’origine, d’âge, de sexe, d’opinion ou de handicap. Il faut veiller à ne pas causer de trouble ou de peines inutiles pour soi et pour autrui.",[],{},[],{"content_title":183,"content_punchline":187,"content_body":194,"content_image":198,"content_link":199},[184],{"type":164,"text":185,"spans":186,"direction":89},"Gi",[],[188],{"type":169,"text":189,"spans":190,"direction":89},"(gui) 義",[191],{"start":192,"end":193,"type":175},6,7,[195],{"type":92,"text":196,"spans":197,"direction":89},"l’honneur, la justice : Le sens de l’honneur ne doit pas être mal placé et servir de prétexte à n’importe quelle action, notamment le duel. Il passe par le respect de soi et des autres. Il implique d’être fidèle à sa parole, à ses engagements et à son idéal. Le sens de gi c’est « avoir le sens du devoir, agir de manière juste ».",[],{},[],{"content_title":201,"content_punchline":205,"content_body":210,"content_image":214,"content_link":215},[202],{"type":164,"text":203,"spans":204,"direction":89},"Rei",[],[206],{"type":169,"text":207,"spans":208,"direction":89},"(lei) 礼",[209],{"start":192,"end":193,"type":175},[211],{"type":92,"text":212,"spans":213,"direction":89},"l’étiquette, la courtoisie : La politesse n’est que l’expression de l’intérêt sincère porté à autrui, quelle que soit sa position sociale, au travers des gestes et des d’attitudes pleines de respect. Le cérémonial et l’étiquette font partie de l’extériorisation de la politesse. Ils servent à offrir un cadre dans lequel le rapport aux autres, au dojo, à l’enseignant, est agréable et harmonieux.",[],{},[],{"content_title":217,"content_punchline":221,"content_body":226,"content_image":230,"content_link":231},[218],{"type":164,"text":219,"spans":220,"direction":89},"Chi",[],[222],{"type":169,"text":223,"spans":224,"direction":89},"(tchi) 智",[225],{"start":193,"end":173,"type":175},[227],{"type":92,"text":228,"spans":229,"direction":89},"la sagesse, l’intelligence au sens de discernement : La sagesse est l’aptitude à n’accorder aux choses et aux évènements que l’importance qu’ils ont réellement, sans passion qui trouble le jugement. La sérénité qui en résulte permet de distinguer le positif et le négatif de toutes choses ou évènements, ce qui est une forme d’intelligence.",[],{},[],{"content_title":233,"content_punchline":237,"content_body":242,"content_image":246,"content_link":247},[234],{"type":164,"text":235,"spans":236,"direction":89},"Shin",[],[238],{"type":169,"text":239,"spans":240,"direction":89},"(chine) 信",[241],{"start":173,"end":174,"type":175},[243],{"type":92,"text":244,"spans":245,"direction":89},"la confiance, la sincérité : Elle est fondamentale dans les arts martiaux. Sans elle la pratique n’est qu’une simulation, voire une gesticulation inutile. Si on n’est pas sincère dans son travail, son respect aux autres, ses attaques, on se ment et on ne permet pas aux autres de progresser. L’engagement doit être total, permanent, sans équivoque, car nous savons tous que l’illusion ne peut perdurer longtemps devant les exigences et le réalisme de la voie, et le regard des autres.",[],{},[],"focus_content$1d6a1d69-a9fe-4074-a2a8-f8e4fd4fae05",{"variation":107,"version":108,"items":250,"primary":251,"id":295,"slice_type":146,"slice_label":5},[],{"anchor":252,"title":253,"sub_title":254,"content":258,"image":259,"liens":260,"details":261,"iframe":5},"arriere",[],[255],{"type":154,"text":256,"spans":257,"direction":89},"Les 2 plis à l'arrière du hakama",[],[],{},[],[262,278],{"content_title":263,"content_punchline":267,"content_body":272,"content_image":276,"content_link":277},[264],{"type":164,"text":265,"spans":266,"direction":89},"Chu",[],[268],{"type":169,"text":269,"spans":270,"direction":89},"(tchū) 忠",[271],{"start":193,"end":173,"type":175},[273],{"type":92,"text":274,"spans":275,"direction":89},"La loyauté, le respect : Voilà bien une valeur en voie de disparition dans notre société contemporaine, alors que l’argent ou les attraits du pouvoir permettent d’acheter les consciences et donc les loyautés. Cette valeur est pourtant la clé de voûte de nos arts martiaux : loyauté envers son professeur, envers les règles internes de son école, envers ses aînés, envers son dojo, envers ses armes et ses habits, envers le kamiza, et bien sûr envers le fondateur. C’est là le reflet de la rectitude du corps et de l’esprit du pratiquant.",[],{},[],{"content_title":279,"content_punchline":283,"content_body":289,"content_image":293,"content_link":294},[280],{"type":164,"text":281,"spans":282,"direction":89},"Ko",[],[284],{"type":169,"text":285,"spans":286,"direction":89},"(ko) 孝",[287],{"start":288,"end":192,"type":175},5,[290],{"type":92,"text":291,"spans":292,"direction":89},"La piété au sens filial (respect de la filiation, de l’héritage reçu): Il n’est pas question de religion ici, sinon nous serions dans les affres des luttes qui vont avec. Il faut comprendre piété dans le sens de respect profond et authentique des bases techniques, des codes, de son art martial, des aspects spirituel, historique et philosophique qui sous-tendent l’Aïkido.",[],{},[],"focus_content$362d2f28-6fe6-4dad-bbbe-9cd8813c3add",{"variation":107,"version":108,"items":297,"primary":298,"id":316,"slice_type":146,"slice_label":5},[],{"anchor":299,"title":300,"sub_title":301,"content":305,"image":312,"liens":313,"details":314,"iframe":315},"mettre",[],[302],{"type":154,"text":303,"spans":304,"direction":89},"Comment mettre le hakama",[],[306,309],{"type":92,"text":307,"spans":308,"direction":89},"Votre hakama peut être porté de plusieurs façons.",[],{"type":92,"text":310,"spans":311,"direction":89},"Voici une vidéo vous expliquant une méthode rapide de le mettre (sans passer les sangles dans la ceinture).",[],{},[],[],"\u003Ciframe width=\"100%\" height=\"315\" src=\"https:\u002F\u002Fwww.youtube.com\u002Fembed\u002FbTxgMlwNc-Q?si=Yr4nBV2wjkUzSBUA\" title=\"Mettre le hakama\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share\" allowfullscreen=\"\">\u003C\u002Fiframe>","focus_content$cf913d90-0f64-4509-85d9-f90db31f9282",{"variation":107,"version":108,"items":318,"primary":319,"id":340,"slice_type":146,"slice_label":5},[],{"anchor":320,"title":321,"sub_title":322,"content":326,"image":330,"liens":337,"details":338,"iframe":339},"plier",[],[323],{"type":154,"text":324,"spans":325,"direction":89},"Comment plier le hakama",[],[327],{"type":92,"text":328,"spans":329,"direction":89},"Apprenez à plier correctement votre hakama",[],{"dimensions":331,"alt":5,"copyright":5,"url":334,"id":335,"edit":336},{"width":332,"height":333},568,426,"https:\u002F\u002Fimages.prismic.io\u002Faikido-traditionnel-cotiere\u002Faf9VhqYofJOwHCJb_hakama.jpg?auto=format,compress","af9VhqYofJOwHCJb",{"x":26,"y":26,"zoom":27,"background":28},[],[],"\u003Ciframe width=\"100%\" height=\"315\" src=\"https:\u002F\u002Fwww.youtube.com\u002Fembed\u002Fn6APGiqhrXY?si=cGpdU45cKHOl-F8p\" title=\"Plier le hakama\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share\" allowfullscreen=\"\">\u003C\u002Fiframe>","focus_content$c0492e5e-1899-4586-a355-d8cbb7041495",{},1782890233769]